               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. SLEIGH</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Have you got the trust-deed of the Company? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I have—the bouse is in the parish of St. Mary Abbotts Kensington—I had been to the houses about a month before.</p>
